---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms governing the use of weknowthewhy.com and WKTW services."
>
  <Section band="deep" class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto prose-invert">
      <h1 class="mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-secondary-text text-sm mb-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-secondary-text leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Agreement</h2>
          <p>By using weknowthewhy.com, you agree to these terms. If you don't agree, please don't use the site.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Services</h2>
          <p>WKTW provides website auditing, content analysis, and digital growth consulting services. Specific service terms are defined in individual engagement agreements.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Free scans</h2>
          <p>Free scans are provided as-is for informational purposes. They represent a subset of our full audit capabilities. Scan results do not constitute professional advice or guarantee specific outcomes.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Intellectual property</h2>
          <p>All content, tools, methodologies, and deliverables produced by WKTW remain the intellectual property of We Know The Why unless explicitly transferred in a client engagement agreement.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p>WKTW provides diagnostic and advisory services. We are not liable for implementation decisions made based on our findings. Revenue impact estimates are projections based on available data, not guarantees.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Changes</h2>
          <p>We may update these terms as our services evolve. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of updated terms.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about these terms? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
